description: A file containing documents concerning Anglo-Soviet church-state relations. The file includes a note about plans for members of a British Quaker organisation to visit the Soviet Union; a letter from the British embassy in Moscow reporting on the visit of the British Quakers; notes on a visit to Moscow and to the Theological Academy at Zagorsk by the bishop of Fulham; and the text of a statement made by the Archbishop of Canterbury on the war in Vietnam. The file also includes notes on a conversation between the Anglican chaplain of Helsinki and the bishop of Zaraisk; notes on Soviet government claims to English churches in Russia; a discussion on claims to an English church in Riga; and a discussion of reclaiming the building of the Church of Saint Andrew in Moscow, a former English church used by the Anglican community there.
